(3, 'Beach Clean-Up', 'Join us for a beach clean-up event where volunteers will help collect trash and debris along the shoreline. This initiative aims to create awareness about ocean pollution and its impact on marine life. Volunteers will receive refreshments and a certificate of appreciation. Bring your friends and family for a day of fun and service!', '2024-11-05 08:00:00', 'Kochi Beach', 'beach_cleanup.jpg'),
(4, 'Kochi Marathon', 'Participate in the Kochi Marathon as a volunteer and support thousands of runners. Help with registration, hydration stations, and cheering on participants. This is a great opportunity to meet new people and enjoy a vibrant atmosphere while promoting health and fitness in our community.', '2024-11-12 06:00:00', 'Marine Drive, Kochi', 'kochi_marathon.jpg'),
(8, 'Tree Plantation Drive', 'Get your hands dirty for a good cause! Join our tree plantation drive aimed at enhancing green cover in our city. Volunteers will plant saplings in designated areas and learn about the importance of trees in combating climate change. All necessary materials will be provided.', '2024-11-18 09:00:00', 'Kochi City Park', 'tree_plantation.jpg'),
(11, 'Food Distribution Campaign', 'Be a part of our food distribution campaign to feed the homeless and underprivileged. Volunteers will help prepare meals and distribute them across various locations in Kochi. This event aims to tackle hunger and bring joy to those in need. Every helping hand counts!', '2024-11-20 11:00:00', 'Kochi Central Station', 'food_distribution.jpg'),
(12, 'Health Awareness Camp', 'Join our health awareness camp where volunteers will assist in conducting free health check-ups for the local community. This event focuses on educating people about healthy living, nutrition, and preventive healthcare. Training will be provided to all volunteers.', '2024-11-25 10:00:00', 'Kochi Community Hall', 'health_camp.jpg'),
(16, 'Skill Development Workshop', 'Help organize a skill development workshop for youth in our community. Volunteers will assist in facilitating various skill sessions ranging from cooking to computer literacy. This event empowers individuals to enhance their skills and improve employability.', '2024-12-01 09:00:00', 'Kochi Youth Center', 'skill_development.jpg'),
(19, 'Cultural Festival', 'Celebrate the rich cultural heritage of Kerala by volunteering at our annual cultural festival. Help with event logistics, stage management, and audience engagement. Experience the vibrant performances, food stalls, and traditional crafts while serving your community.', '2024-12-10 16:00:00', 'Fort Kochi', 'cultural_festival.jpg'),
(22, 'Charity Sports Day', 'Join us for a Charity Sports Day where volunteers will help organize various sports events for children from underprivileged backgrounds. Assist in setting up games, distributing prizes, and cheering for the participants. Your support can make a big difference in their lives!', '2024-12-15 08:00:00', 'Kochi Sports Complex', 'sports_day.jpg'),
(26, 'Animal Welfare Awareness', 'Get involved in our animal welfare awareness campaign aimed at promoting the well-being of stray animals. Volunteers will help distribute food, provide medical assistance, and educate the public on responsible pet ownership and animal rights.', '2024-12-20 09:00:00', 'Kochi Animal Shelter', 'animal_welfare.jpg'),
(30, 'Womens Empowerment Seminar', 'Volunteer at our Womens Empowerment Seminar aimed at educating and inspiring women in our community. Help with registration, event coordination, and facilitating discussions. This seminar will feature guest speakers sharing their success stories and insights.', '2024-12-25 10:00:00', 'Kochi Convention Center', 'women_empowerment.jpg'),
(34, 'Christmas Gift Distribution', 'Spread joy this Christmas by volunteering for our gift distribution event. Help wrap and distribute gifts to children in need. This event aims to bring smiles and hope to underprivileged kids during the festive season. Every little contribution matters!', '2024-12-26 14:00:00', 'Kochi Town Hall', 'christmas_distribution.jpg'),
(38, 'Yoga Camp', 'Join us as a volunteer for a community yoga camp focusing on mental and physical wellness. Assist in setting up yoga mats, coordinating sessions, and providing refreshments. Participants will learn about the benefits of yoga for a balanced lifestyle.', '2024-12-28 06:00:00', 'Kochi Beach', 'yoga_camp.jpg'),
(42, 'Disaster Management Training', 'Become a part of our disaster management training program aimed at equipping volunteers with essential skills to respond effectively during emergencies. Participants will learn first aid, rescue operations, and safety protocols. Your involvement can help save lives!', '2024-12-30 09:00:00', 'Kochi Fire Station', 'disaster_management.jpg'),
(46, 'Kochi Literature Festival', 'Join us in organizing the Kochi Literature Festival! Volunteers will help with various tasks including guest management, logistics, and attendee engagement. Experience the world of literature and interact with renowned authors and poets in a vibrant atmosphere.', '2025-01-05 10:00:00', 'Kochi International Book Fair', 'literature_festival.jpg'),
(3, 'Street Art Festival', 'Be a part of our Street Art Festival celebrating local artists and their creativity. Volunteers will assist in setting up art installations, organizing workshops, and guiding visitors. This event aims to promote art and culture in our community while supporting local talents.', '2025-01-10 11:00:00', 'Kochi City Streets', 'street_art_festival.jpg'),
(4, 'Environmental Awareness Rally', 'Join our rally to promote environmental awareness in Kochi. Volunteers will help distribute pamphlets, organize activities, and engage with the community to educate them about sustainability practices. Be a voice for our planet and inspire others!', '2025-01-15 08:00:00', 'Kochi Town Square', 'environmental_rally.jpg'),
(8, 'Heritage Walk', 'Volunteer for a guided heritage walk through the historical sites of Kochi. Assist in engaging participants with stories of our past and promoting local culture. This event aims to raise awareness about preserving our heritage while enjoying a beautiful walk.', '2025-01-20 17:00:00', 'Kochi Fort', 'heritage_walk.jpg'),
(11, 'Photography Workshop', 'Join us as a volunteer for a photography workshop aimed at helping aspiring photographers enhance their skills. Assist with setting up equipment, coordinating sessions, and facilitating discussions. Capture the beauty of Kochi while sharing your passion for photography!', '2025-01-25 09:00:00', 'Kochi Art Gallery', 'photography_workshop.jpg'),
(12, 'Food Fest', 'Help organize a vibrant food fest showcasing the diverse culinary delights of Kerala. Volunteers will assist with logistics, setting up food stalls, and ensuring a smooth experience for visitors. Experience delicious food while contributing to this exciting event!', '2025-01-30 12:00:00', 'Kochi Marine Drive', 'food_fest.jpg'),
(16, 'Street Music Festival', 'Join us for a street music festival celebrating local musicians and their talents. Volunteers will assist in setting up stages, managing sound equipment, and ensuring a lively atmosphere. Experience the joy of music while supporting our local artists!', '2025-02-05 18:00:00', 'Kochi Town Center', 'music_festival.jpg'),
(19, 'Kochi Art Exhibition', 'Be a part of our annual art exhibition showcasing local artists. Volunteers will help with setup, registration, and guiding visitors through the exhibition. This event aims to promote art and creativity in our community while supporting local talent.', '2025-02-10 10:00:00', 'Kochi Museum', 'art_exhibition.jpg'),
(22, 'Family Fun Day', 'Join us for a Family Fun Day filled with games, activities, and entertainment for all ages. Volunteers will help organize games, set up booths, and engage with families. This event aims to promote family bonding and community spirit!', '2025-02-15 11:00:00', 'Kochi Park', 'family_fun_day.jpg'),
(26, 'Sustainable Living Workshop', 'Help organize a workshop focused on sustainable living practices. Volunteers will assist in facilitating sessions, providing materials, and promoting eco-friendly habits. This event aims to educate participants on reducing their carbon footprint and living sustainably.', '2025-02-20 09:00:00', 'Kochi Eco Center', 'sustainable_living.jpg'),
(30, 'Kochi Fashion Show', 'Be a part of the Kochi Fashion Show where local designers showcase their talent. Volunteers will help with logistics, backstage management, and audience engagement. Experience the glamour and creativity of the fashion world while supporting local designers!', '2025-02-25 17:00:00', 'Kochi Convention Center', 'fashion_show.jpg'),
(34, 'Outdoor Adventure Camp', 'Join us as a volunteer for an outdoor adventure camp aimed at youth. Help organize activities such as rock climbing, hiking, and team-building exercises. This event promotes physical fitness and teamwork while providing a fun experience for participants!', '2025-03-01 08:00:00', 'Kochi Adventure Park', 'adventure_camp.jpg'),
(38, 'Pet Adoption Drive', 'Volunteer at our pet adoption drive aimed at finding loving homes for stray animals. Assist with registration, showcasing pets, and providing information to potential adopters. This event helps promote animal welfare and encourages responsible pet ownership.', '2025-03-05 10:00:00', 'Kochi Animal Shelter', 'pet_adoption.jpg'),
(42, 'Gardening Workshop', 'Join us for a gardening workshop where participants will learn about sustainable gardening practices. Volunteers will assist in organizing the workshop, providing materials, and engaging with participants. This event aims to promote green living and environmental consciousness!', '2025-03-10 09:00:00', 'Kochi Botanical Garden', 'gardening_workshop.jpg'),
(46, 'Science Fair', 'Be a part of our annual science fair showcasing innovative projects by students. Volunteers will help with setup, registration, and guiding visitors. This event encourages creativity and scientific exploration among young minds in our community.', '2025-03-15 10:00:00', 'Kochi School Auditorium', 'science_fair.jpg'),
